- Documented the requirement in [`docs/docker-compose.md`](/Z:/_Dev/AI-agents/monagentjava/docs/docker-compose.md)

Default local value:
```yaml
OPENSEARCH_INITIAL_ADMIN_PASSWORD: ${OPENSEARCH_INITIAL_ADMIN_PASSWORD:-admin123!}
```

That should stop the container from exiting with:
- `No custom admin password found`

If you want to use your own password instead of the default, set it before starting:
```bash
export OPENSEARCH_INITIAL_ADMIN_PASSWORD='your-strong-password'
docker compose --profile observability up --build
```

